Summary of Amendments Adopted by Senate
Committee Amendments Proposed by Senate Committee on Finance to the original
bill
1. Require the monies deposited into the La. Early Childhood Education Fund
be 25% of the net mobile sports wagering proceeds.
2. Remove the $20 million floor on the amount credited to the La. Early
Childhood Education Fund.
3. Remove the requirement that the deposit to the La. Early Childhood
Education Fund equal the greater of 25% of collections or $20 million.
4. Require a $20 million cap on the amount credited to the Supporting
Programs, Opportunities, Resources, and Teams Fund.
5. Change the effective date from July 1, 2026 to July 1, 2027.
6. Make technical changes.
